      tasks:
      - name: check-traffic
        template: check-traffic
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: destination
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.destination }}'

  - name: check-traffic
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: destination
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/checktraffic?destination={{inputs.parameters.destination}}"
      method: GET
    outputs:
      parameters:
      - name: traffic_condition
        valueFrom:
          jsonPath: "$.traffic_condition"

  - name: get-traffic-update
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: location
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/gettrafficupdate?location={{inputs.parameters.location}}"
      method: GET
    outputs:
      parameters:
      - name: trafficDelay
        valueFrom:
          jsonPath: "$.trafficDelay"

  - name: calculate-travel-time
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: flightTimes
      - name: trafficDelay
        value: '{{ tasks.get-traffic-update.outputs.parameters.trafficDelay }}'
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/calculatetraveltime?flightTimes={{inputs.parameters.flightTimes}}&trafficDelay={{inputs.parameters.trafficDelay}}"
      method: GET
    outputs:
      parameters:
      - name: travelTime
        valueFrom:
          jsonPath: "$.travelTime"

  - name: alert-before-departure
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: event_time
      - name: travel_time
        value: '{{ tasks.calculate-travel-time.outputs.parameters.travelTime }}'
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/alertbeforedeparture?event_time={{inputs.parameters.event_time}}&travel_time={{inputs.parameters.travel_time}}"
      method: GET
    outputs:
